<i>adjective</i>: 흐늘흐늘하다 [흐늘흐늘하다], 하늘하늘하다 [하늘하늘하다], 물컹하다 [물컹하다], 물컹물컹하다 [물컹물컹하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>흐늘흐늘하다 [흐늘흐늘하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. soft; wavy; floaty</dd><br>
<dd>힘없이 늘어져 자꾸 흔들릴 정도로 가볍고 부드럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Light and soft to the extent of drooping feebly and swaying repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. spongy; pulpy; squashy</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 자꾸 뭉크러지거나 흔들릴 정도로 단단하지 못하다.</dd><br>
<dd>An object being soft-textured so that it keeps swaying or cannot hold its shape.</dd><br>
<dt>하늘하늘하다 [하늘하늘하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. fluttering; wavy; floaty</dd><br>
<dd>힘없이 늘어져 계속해서 흔들릴 정도로 가볍고 부드럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Light and soft to the extent of drooping feebly and swaying repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. spongy; pulpy; squashy</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 계속해서 뭉개지거나 흔들릴 정도로 단단하지 못하다.</dd><br>
<dd>An object being soft-textured so that it repeatedly sways or cannot hold its shape.</dd><br>
<dt>물컹하다 [물컹하다]</dt><br>
<dd>squashy; mushy</dd><br>
<dd>뭉그러질 정도로 물렁하다.</dd><br>
<dd>So soft as to be mushy.</dd><br>
<dt>물컹물컹하다 [물컹물컹하다]</dt><br>
<dd>squashy</dd><br>
<dd>뭉그러질 정도로 여기저기가 물렁하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling so soft as to be mushy here and there.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>